{"id":113,"parent_id":95,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":113,"title":"Acts 18","subtitle":"","short_title":"Acts","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 18"],[".studySummary",["i","Being rejected by the Jews, Paul turns to the Gentiles—He preaches, ministers, and travels—Apollos also preaches with power."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.1","order":"03.07.018.13852"},["b","1"],"After these things Paul departed from Athens, and came to Corinth;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.2","order":"03.07.018.13853"},["b","2"],"And found a certain Jew named",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Aquila"],", born in Pontus, lately come from Italy, with his wife Priscilla; (because that Claudius had commanded all Jews to depart from Rome:) and came unto them."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.3","order":"03.07.018.13854"},["b","3"],"And because he was of the same craft, he abode with them, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"wrought"],": for by their occupation they were",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"tentmakers"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.4","order":"03.07.018.13855"},["b","4"],"And he reasoned in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"synagogue"],"every",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"sabbath"],", and persuaded the Jews and the Greeks."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.5","order":"03.07.018.13856"},["b","5"],"And when Silas and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Timotheus"],"were come from Macedonia, Paul was pressed in the spirit, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"testified"],"to the Jews",["i","that"],"Jesus",["i","was"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"Christ"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.6","order":"03.07.018.13857"},["b","6"],"And when they opposed themselves, and blasphemed, he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"shook"],["i","his"],"raiment, and said unto them, Your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"blood"],["i","be"],"upon your own heads; I",["i","am"],"clean: from henceforth I will go unto the Gentiles."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.7","order":"03.07.018.13858"},["b","7"],"¶And he departed thence, and entered into a certain",["i","man’s"],"house, named Justus,",["i","one"],"that worshipped God, whose house joined hard to the synagogue."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.8","order":"03.07.018.13859"},["b","8"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Crispus"],", the chief ruler of the synagogue, believed on the Lord with all his house; and many of the Corinthians hearing",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"believed"],", and were baptized."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.9","order":"03.07.018.13860"},["b","9"],"Then spake the Lord to Paul in the night by a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"vision"],", Be not afraid, but speak, and hold not thy peace:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.10","order":"03.07.018.13861"},["b","10"],"For I am with thee, and no man shall set on thee to hurt thee: for I have much",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"people"],"in this city."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.11","order":"03.07.018.13862"},["b","11"],"And he continued",["i","there"],"a year and six months, teaching the word of God among them."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.12","order":"03.07.018.13863"},["b","12"],"¶And when Gallio was the deputy of Achaia, the Jews made insurrection with one accord against Paul, and brought him to the judgment seat,"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.13","order":"03.07.018.13864"},["b","13"],"Saying, This",["i","fellow"],"persuadeth men to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"worship"],"God contrary to the law."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.14","order":"03.07.018.13865"},["b","14"],"And when Paul was now about to open",["i","his"],"mouth, Gallio said unto the Jews, If it were a matter of wrong or",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"wicked"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"lewdness"],", O",["i","ye"],"Jews, reason would that I should bear with you:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.15","order":"03.07.018.13866"},["b","15"],"But if it be a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"question"],"of words and names, and",["i","of"],"your law, look ye",["i","to it;"],"for I will be no judge of such",["i","matters."]],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.16","order":"03.07.018.13867"},["b","16"],"And he drave them from the judgment seat."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.17","order":"03.07.018.13868"},["b","17"],"Then all the Greeks took Sosthenes, the chief ruler of the synagogue, and beat",["i","him"],"before the judgment seat. And Gallio cared for none of those things."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.18","order":"03.07.018.13869"},["b","18"],"¶And Paul",["i","after this"],"tarried",["i","there"],"yet a good while, and then took his leave of the brethren, and sailed thence into Syria, and with him Priscilla and Aquila; having shorn",["i","his"],"head in Cenchrea: for he had a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"vow"],"."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.19","order":"03.07.018.13870"},["b","19"],"And he came to Ephesus, and left them there: but he himself entered into the synagogue, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"reasoned"],"with the Jews."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.20","order":"03.07.018.13871"},["b","20"],"When they desired",["i","him"],"to tarry longer time with them, he consented not;"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.21","order":"03.07.018.13872"},["b","21"],"But bade them farewell, saying, I must by all means keep this feast that cometh in Jerusalem: but I will return again unto you, if God will. And he sailed from Ephesus."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.22","order":"03.07.018.13873"},["b","22"],"And when he had landed at Cæsarea, and gone up, and saluted the church, he went down to Antioch."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.23","order":"03.07.018.13874"},["b","23"],"And after he had spent some time",["i","there,"],"he departed, and went over",["i","all"],"the country of Galatia and Phrygia in order, strengthening all the disciples."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.24","order":"03.07.018.13875"},["b","24"],"¶And a certain Jew named",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"Apollos"],", born at Alexandria, an eloquent man,",["i","and"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"mighty"],"in the scriptures, came to Ephesus."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.25","order":"03.07.018.13876"},["b","25"],"This man was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"instructed"],"in the way of the Lord; and being",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"fervent"],"in the spirit, he spake and taught",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_25c"},"diligently"],"the things of the Lord, knowing only the baptism of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_25d"},"John"],"."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.26","order":"03.07.018.13877"},["b","26"],"And he began to speak boldly in the synagogue: whom when Aquila and Priscilla had heard, they took him unto",["i","them,"],"and expounded unto him the way of God more perfectly."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.27","order":"03.07.018.13878"},["b","27"],"And when he was disposed to pass into Achaia, the brethren",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"wrote"],", exhorting the disciples to receive him: who, when he was come, helped them much which had believed through grace:"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.28","order":"03.07.018.13879"},["b","28"],"For he mightily convinced the Jews,",["i","and that"],"publickly,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"shewing"],"by the scriptures that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"Jesus was Christ"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.2a","order":"03.07.018.13880"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/16.19"},"1 Cor. 16:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.3a","order":"03.07.018.13882"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/20.34"},"Acts 20:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.9"},"1 Thes. 2:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.3b","order":"03.07.018.13884"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/skill"},"TG Skill"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.4a","order":"03.07.018.13886"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/17.17"},"Acts 17:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/19.8"},"19:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.4b","order":"03.07.018.13888"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sabbath"},"TG Sabbath"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.5a","order":"03.07.018.13890"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/1.1"},"1 Thes. 1:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.5b","order":"03.07.018.13892"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/7.26.16,26"},"Alma 7:26 (16, 26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.5c","order":"03.07.018.13894"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-messiah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Messiah"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.6a","order":"03.07.018.13896"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.14"},"Matt. 10:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/13.51.44-51"},"Acts 13:51 (44–51)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/24.15"},"D&C 24:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/60.15"},"60:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.6b","order":"03.07.018.13898"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.4.3-5"},"Ezek. 33:4 (3–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.8a","order":"03.07.018.13900"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/1.14"},"1 Cor. 1:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.8b","order":"03.07.018.13902"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism-qualifications-for"},"TG Baptism, Qualifications for"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.9a","order":"03.07.018.13904"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-appearances-postmortal"},"TG Jesus Christ, Appearances, Postmortal"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vision"},"Vision"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.10a","order":"03.07.018.13906"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/111.2.2-11"},"D&C 111:2 (2–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.13a","order":"03.07.018.13908"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/30.7.7-11"},"Alma 30:7 (7–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.14a","order":"03.07.018.13910"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/25.5"},"Acts 25:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.14b","order":"03.07.018.13912"},["b","14b"],["span.small","GR"],"crime."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.15a","order":"03.07.018.13914"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.29"},"Acts 23:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.18a","order":"03.07.018.13916"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vow"},"TG Vow"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.19a","order":"03.07.018.13918"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/17.2"},"Acts 17:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.24a","order":"03.07.018.13920"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/16.12"},"1 Cor. 16:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.24b","order":"03.07.018.13922"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.11"},"D&C 100:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.25a","order":"03.07.018.13924"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/education"},"TG Education"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.25b","order":"03.07.018.13926"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zeal"},"TG Zeal"],"."],["div",{"id":"25c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.25c","order":"03.07.018.13928"},["b","25c"],["span.small","GR"],"accurately, precisely, diligently."],["div",{"id":"25d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.25d","order":"03.07.018.13930"},["b","25d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/19.3.3-6"},"Acts 19:3 (3–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.27a","order":"03.07.018.13932"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.11"},"D&C 42:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.28a","order":"03.07.018.13934"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-study-of"},"TG Scriptures, Study of"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.28b","order":"03.07.018.13936"},["b","28b"],["span.small","OR"],"Jesus is the Christ."]]}
